snippet.title: Amber Heard In Trouble! Johnny Depp Sues ACLU And Exposes Elon Musk
snippet.description:
Amber Heard In Trouble! Johnny Depp Sues ACLU And Exposes Elon Musk
Subscribe Here 👉 http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3hHTptI

After Amber Heard pledged to donate her 7 million dollar divorce settlement to the ACLU Johnny Depp’s lawyers argued that she never followed through with it. Now Johnny Depp’s legal team has decided to call out the American Civil Liberties Union with the hopes of revealing the real donation that Amber made. Not only that but Depp’s team believes that Elon Musk may have actually made the donation on her behalf.

SOURCE: https://www.tmz.com/2021/05/19/johnny-depp-sues-aclu-amber-heard-donation-elon-musk/
